fields.description: SMB authentication methods supported by server. Valid values are NTLMv2, Kerberos. Should be passed as a string with delimiter ';'.
fields.name: AuthenticationMethods

fields.description: SMB channel encryption supported by server. Valid values are AES-128-CCM, AES-128-GCM, AES-256-GCM. Should be passed as a string with delimiter ';'.
fields.name: ChannelEncryption

fields.description: Kerberos ticket encryption supported by server. Valid values are RC4-HMAC, AES-256. Should be passed as a string with delimiter ';'
fields.name: KerberosTicketEncryption

fields.description: Multichannel setting. Applies to Premium FileStorage only.
fields.name: Multichannel

fields.description: SMB protocol versions supported by server. Valid values are SMB2.1, SMB3.0, SMB3.1.1. Should be passed as a string with delimiter ';'.
fields.name: Versions
